quran[98]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaaf, Haa, Yaa, ʿAyn, Ṣaad"
  19,2,"Woto yaa fo Soabã yolsg A sẽn maan n kõ A yambã a Zakariyaa wã lɑ D togsd foo."
  19,3,"A sẽn wa n bool a Soabã ne solgre."
  19,4,"N yeele:"" m Soaba! m kõbã valemsame, tɩ mam zugã puk ne peelem; m Soaba! m pa yɩ n kos Foom me n kong ye''."
  19,5,"La mam yaeesda pẽdbã ledsgã mam kũum poorẽ, lɑ mam pagã yaa pʋg-kir n pa rogdẽ ye, bɩ F kõ maam lεdsd sẽn yi Fo nengẽ sẽn yaa biig tɩ sõngd-mɑ."
  19,6,"T'a rɩkd mam faado, la a rɩk a Yakuub zakã rãmb faado, la maan-a m Soaba! t'a yɩ b sẽn yard-ɑ soɑbɑ."
  19,7,"(Yaa foo a) Zakariyaɑ, Tõnd na n nooga fo sũur ne biiga, a yʋʋr la a Yahyaa, Tõnd pɑ mɑɑn sẽn dɑ loog tɩ b pʋd ɑ yʋʋrã buud ye."
  19,8,"La a [ Zakariya ] yeel yã: m Soaba! yɩta wãn tɩ mam paam biiga, tɩ mam pagã yaa kiri, la ma me yaool n taa kʋʋlem tεkẽ."
  19,9,"La ɑ [mɑlεkã[ yeel yã: ""yellã yaa wɑ fo sẽn togsã! Lɑ fo Soabã yeelame t'ɑ yaa yol-yol ne Yẽ; lɑ ad Mam da naana foom sẽn dɑ loog tɩ fo ra pa yɩ n yɑ fʋɩ ye."
  19,10,"La a yeel yã: "" m Soaba! maan ɑ tagmas n kõ maam tɩ m bãnge"". lɑ A yeel yã (biigã paoong) tagmasã yaa fo sẽn na n wɑ ka tõe n gom ne nebã yʋnd a tãab lɑ f tɑr laafɩ""."
  19,11,"T'a yi Mĩhrẽ wã n kẽng ɑ nebẽ wã n yeel-b ne teesg tɩ b yɩlg A yʋʋrã zaabr la yibeoogo."
  19,12,"Yahyaa, gãd Gafã (Taooraatã) ne nidg pãnga, la Tõnd kõ-a-la bãngrã t'a nɑn yaɑ bilfu."
  19,13,"(N leb n kõ-a) nimbãan-zoeer sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ, la yɩlgre; A leb n yɩɩme n ya wẽn-zoεta."
  19,14,"N yɑ manegd n tʋgd a roagdb a yiibã, a pa yɩ waoog-m-meng soab n yɑɑ Wẽnd-kɩɩs ye."
  19,15,"Lɑ tɩlgr be ne-a a rogem raare, la a kũum raare, la raar ning b sẽn na n vʋʋg-a t'ɑ yɑɑ vɩtã."
  19,16,"Lɑ tẽeg Gafã (Kʋrãanã) pʋgẽ, a Maryam yelle, a sẽn wa n lak n bɑs a zakã rãmb n tees wĩntoog sẽn pukdẽ."
  19,17,"N maan lill n yi-ba, tɩ Tõnd na n tʋms Gibriil tɩ kẽng a nengẽ t'a maan a meng n lebg ninsaal fɑs."
  19,18,"Ta a (Maryam) yeele: ""mam kota gũudum ne Yolsg nɑɑbã n yi foom tɩ f sã n zoeta Wẽnde."
  19,19,"La a yeel yã: ""ad mam yaa fo Soabã tẽn-tʋʋma, n na n wa kõ foom bi-yɩlenga""."
  19,20,"La a yeel yã:"" mam na n yɩɩ wãn n paam biig tɩ sɩd pa pẽneg mɑɑm m leb n pa yɩ yoaad me?"""
  19,21,"T'a yeele: ""yaa woto wɑ fo sẽn yeelã! Lɑ fo Soabã yeelame: "" woto yaa yol-yol ne Maam, la sẽn na yɩl tɩ d maan-ɑ tɩ yaa yel-solemd ne nebã la yolsg sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ, la ɑd yaa pʋleng sẽn zoe n yɩ."""
  19,22,"T'a rɩk ɑ pʋgã n kẽng ne-ɑ zĩig sẽn zãre."
  19,23,"Tɩ rogmã zabdem tɑll-ɑ n tʋg Tɑmɑr-tɩɩgã sεεgẽ, ɑ yeelɑme: "" kɑto ! Mam sã n da kiẽ taoor tɩ wã pɑ wɑ pɑ são, tɩ mɑm lebg yell b sẽn yĩmi!"""
  19,24,"T'ɑ (ɭɩsɑ) bool-a ɑ tẽngrã [n yeele:] ""ra sãam f sũur ye. Ad fo Soabã maana ko-sor fo tẽngrã."
  19,25,"Lɑ f Miim Tɑmɑr-tɩigã yẽgre tɩ tamarʋ maas n na n dʋʋg f nengẽ tɩ yaa sẽn wob pɑɑlem."
  19,26,"Bi f rɩ la f yũ la noog f sũuri. Fo sã n wa tʋg n yã ned t'ɑ sok-fo, bɩ f yeel ad mam rɩkɑ pʋleng ne Yolsg naabã sĩndg no-loeere, rẽnd m kõn tol n gom rũndɑ ne ned ye."
  19,27,"T'a tall-a (biigã) n kẽng a nebẽ wã, tɩ b yeel-a:"" ad fo wa ne yell kãseng sẽn yɑɑ zɩlembeedo."
  19,28,"A Harʋʋn tão wã, fo saambã pa yɩ nin-wẽng ye, fo ma wã me pa yɩ yoaad-poak ye."
  19,29,"T'a tees-a [biigã], la b yeel yã: ""tõnd nɑ n gomɑ ne biig sẽn be zεgsẽ wãn-wãnɑ?"
  19,30,"La a [biigã] yeel yã: "" ad mam yaa Wẽnd yamba, A kõo maam Gafã lɑ A leb n maan maam tɩ m yaa nabiyaama,"
  19,31,"La A maan maam tɩ mam tar bark mam sẽn be zĩig ning fãa, la A sagl maam ne pʋʋsg la zak tɩ mam sã n ket n vʋɩ."
  19,32,"N yɑɑ mɑnegd ne m mɑ wã, A ka maan maam tɩ m yaa waoog-n-meng soab n yaa zu-be-ned ye."
  19,33,"Lɑ tɩlgr be ne maam m rogem raare, la m kũum raare la raar ning b sẽn na n vʋʋg-ma yikrã raarã."
  19,34,"Yaa woto la a Yiisa sẽn yaa a Maryam biigã, yaa sɩd koεεgã lɑ woto pɑ bãmb sẽn be a soɑb pʋgẽ n maand sik ɑ yellã pʋgẽ wã ye."
  19,35,"Pa sõmb ne Wẽnd t'A tall biig buud ye, A yɩlgɑme n yi rẽ, A sã n bʋ yelle, A yet-a lame: ""yɩ!"" t'a be yɩɩbẽ."
  19,36,"Lɑ ɑd yaa Wẽnd la mam Soaba; n leb n yaa yãmb Soabã. Bɩ y tũ-A, tɩ wãnde lɑ sor sẽn yɑ tɩrga."
  19,37,"Tɩ sulã yõs taab bãmb ne taab sʋka, rẽnd wɩɩbd be ne sẽn kɩfl-bã, sẽn yɑɑ ra-kãsengã raar yel-yɩtsã."
  19,38,"B wʋmb kɑ to b yãɑb me pɑ tɑr to rɑɑr ning b sẽn na n wa Tõnd nengẽ wã! La ad rũndã wẽgdbã bee meneng sẽn yaa vẽeneg pʋgẽ."
  19,39,"La bugs-b ne nĩmsã raarã, yellã sẽn wat n bʋ wã; tɩ bãmb yaool n be yam yaal-yaal pʋgẽ n ka kõt sɩd ye."
  19,40,"Ad yaa Tõnd n rɩkd tẽngã faad la bũmb nins sẽn be a zugã fãa faado, la b lebgr zĩig me yaa Tõnd nengẽ."
  19,41,"La f tẽeg Gafã pʋgẽ a ɭbraahɩɩm yelle, ad a yɩɩ sɩd soab n yɑɑ nabiyaamã;"
  19,42,"A sẽn wa n yeel a saambã: ""m saamba, yaa bõe tɩ fo tũud bũmb sẽn pa wʋmd la ɑ pa ne, la a pa tõe n naf foom n yi baa fʋɩ?"
  19,43,"M saamba, ad mam paama bãngr fo sẽn pa tare, bi f pʋg maam tɩ m kãndg foom sor sẽn yaa tɩrga."
  19,44,"M saamba, ra tũ a Sʋtãan ye, ad a yɩɩme n yɑɑ dũni Yolsg naabã kɩɩsda."
  19,45,"Yaa m saamba, ad mam yaeesdame nang nɑ n wa paam foom sẽn yi dũni yolsg naabã nengẽ, tɩ fo wa yɩ a sʋtãan lallda."
  19,46,"Lɑ ɑ yeel yã : ""Fo kisɑ mam soaben-dãmbã! foo ɑ ɭbraahɩɩmã? Fo sã n pa tek n bas (tõnd rʋbsã sãbsgo) m na lob foom ne kuga, lɑ pʋs n wãag n bas maam wakat wooko""."
  19,47,"La a yeel yã:""tɩlgr be ne foom, m na wa n kos m Soabã t'A yaaf-fo, mam Soabã yaa manegd ne maam""."
  19,48,"La m lak n basa yãmb ne bũmb nins yãmb sẽn tũud zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã fãa. M tũuda m Soabã A ye, tɩ sãnd-sãnde m kõ n tol n kos m Soabã n kong n wɑ yɩ zu-be-ned ye""."
  19,49,"La a sẽn wa n lak n bas-b la bũmb nins b sẽn tũud zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã, Tõnd kõ-a-la a ɭshaak la a Yaakuuba, la b fãa gilli Tõnd maan-b lame tɩ b yaa nabiyaam-dãmba."
  19,50,"La Tõnd kõ-b-la bũmb sẽn yi Tõnd yolsgã pʋgẽ, la D maan yʋ-noog sẽn zẽk b yĩngɑ."
  19,51,"Le tẽeg Gafã pʋgẽ a Musa yelle, ad a yɩɩ pʋ-peelem soaba, n yaa tʋntʋʋm n yaa nabiyaama."
  19,52,"Tɩ Tõnd bool-a Tʋʋr tãngã rɩtg wεεngẽ, lɑ D pẽneg-ɑ ne sõsgɑ."
  19,53,"La D leb n kõ-a sẽn yi Tõnd yolsgã pʋgẽ, n maan a ma-biig a Haarʋʋn t'a yaa nabiyaama."
  19,54,"Le tẽeg Gafã pʋga a ɭsmaa'ɩɩl yelle, ad a yɩɩ pʋleng pidsda, n leb n ya tẽn-tʋʋmã n ya nabiyaama."
  19,55,"A ra sagenda a zakã rãmb ne Pʋʋsg la zak yãkre, a leb n da tara yard a Soabã nengẽ."
  19,56,"Tẽeg Gafã pʋga a ɭdrɩɩsa, ad a yɩɩ sɩd soab n ya nabiyaama."
  19,57,"Tɩ Tõnd zẽk ɑ yʋʋrã t'ɑ ziirã zẽke."
  19,58,"Ad bãmbã la Wẽnd sẽn maan-b rãmb neema wã, sẽn yi nabiyaam-rãmbã pʋgẽ, sẽn yi a Adam koɑmbẽ la neb nins Tõnd sẽn rɩk n naag a Nuuh koglgã pʋgẽ wã, la sẽn yi a ɭbraahɩɩm la a ɭsraa'ɩɩl koɑmbẽ lɑ neb nins Tõnd sẽn kãndg la D tũusã pʋgẽ, b sã n wa karemd Arrɑhmɑɑn nɑɑb Aayayã b nengẽ, la b sẽn lʋɩt n maan suguud n kũmdẽ۩."
  19,59,"Tɩ lεdsdb leds bãmb poorẽ, n yeeb Pʋʋsgã la b tũ b yõyã yamleoodo, lɑ yi bilf bala b na yek wẽng Gεhɑnnɑm pʋgẽ"
  19,60,"Rẽnda ned ning sẽn tuub la a kõ sɩda la a tʋm tʋʋm sõmse, ad bãmbã rãmbã na n kẽe arzãna, b pa na n wẽg-b baa fʋɩ."
  19,61,"Ãrzãn ning yolsg naab sẽn pʋlem A yembsã ne lilli, ad A pʋlengã yaa sẽn na n wa."
  19,62,"B pa wʋmd ɑ pʋgẽ gom-zɑɑl rẽnda tɩlgr koεεg bɑlɑ, lɑ b tara b rɩtl a pʋgẽ yibeoog la zaabre."
  19,63,"Ad ɑrzẽn ning sẽn sɩf woto wã, yẽ la Tõnd sẽn rɩkd a faad n kõt D yembsã, yembs nins sẽn yɑ-b wẽn-zoetbã."
  19,64,"Lɑ Mɑlεk-rãmb pa sikd rẽnda ne fo Soabã saglgo, bũmb ning sẽn be tõnd taoore, la bũmb ning sẽn be d poorẽ la sẽn be wãndã sʋk yaa Yẽ n so, lɑ fo Soabã pa yɩ n yaa yĩmd ye."
  19,65,"Saasã la tẽngã la bũmb nins sẽn be b yiibã sʋk Soabã, bɩ f tũ-A la f maan sugr ne A tũudmã, rẽ yĩnga fo mii A wõneg bɩɩ? A pɑ tɑr to ye."
  19,66,"La ninsaal yetame: ""rẽ yĩnga mam sã n ki, b na n leb n yika maam ne vɩɩm yεsa?"""
  19,67,"Rẽ yĩnga ninsaal pa tẽr tɩ Tõnd naan-a-lɑ sẽn dɑ looge, t'a ra pa baa fʋɩ?"
  19,68,"Lɑ (m wẽenda) ne fo Soabã, M na n tigim-b lame la sʋtãambã, rẽ poorẽ D na peeg-b n tʋg Gεhannem rɑg-noẽ wã tɩ b yaɑ sẽn wũgi."
  19,69,"Rẽ poorẽ, D na yiis zãma fãa pʋgẽ, neb nins sẽn yɩɩd ne wẽng ne Arahmaan naabã kɩɩsgã."
  19,70,"Rẽ poorẽ, Tõnd n yɩɩd minim ne neb nins sẽn sõmb ne bugmã kõomã."
  19,71,"Ned ka be yãmb sʋk rẽndame t'ɑ pɩʋʋg be [ bugmẽ wã, Gεhãnmã põ zuku ]; ad pɩʋʋg kãngã yaa bũmb ning fo Soabã sẽn bʋ tɩ yɑɑ tɩlɑe."
  19,72,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ D põsg neb nins sẽn zoe Wẽndã la D bas wẽgdbã beenẽ tɩ b yĩga."
  19,73,"Lɑ b sã n wa karemd Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã vẽenese, kɩfr-rãmbã yetda neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã: ""sul a yiibã, ãnd n yɩɩd sõmblem ne zĩiga lɑ zɑgse la ãnd n yɩɩd sõmblem ne zĩid-n-taase?"""
  19,74,"Lɑ sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk tẽms sẽn reng bãmb taoore, tɩ b arzεgs lɑ b gesr neeerem yɩɩd bãmba."
  19,75,"Yeele: ""ned ning sẽn wa n be meneng pʋga, bɩ yolsg nɑabã rõneg ɑ yĩngɑ rõnegr tεkẽ, hal tɩ b sã n wɑ yãnd b sẽn pʋlem-bã, zem tɩ yaa nangã, maa tɩ yaa dũni wã yikri, wakat kãng b na bãng ãnd zĩig wẽng n yɩɩde, la ãnd tã-biis vɑleng n yɩɩde""."
  19,76,"Lɑ Wẽnd paasda neb nins sẽn kãndg-bã ne kãndgre, la yel-sõma sẽn paad n woglã n yɩɩd ne keoor f Soabã nengẽ la b leb n yɩɩd ne bɑɑs neere."
  19,77,"Fo pɑ yã ned ning sẽn kɩfl ne Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã la a yeele: "" ad b na kõ maam koamb la arzεka""."
  19,78,"Rẽ yĩnga a lik n bãngɑ sẽn solgã bɩ a tɑllɑ pʋleng yolsg Naabã nengẽ t'A nɑ n kõ-ɑ-lɑ rẽ?"
  19,79,"Pɑ poto ye! D na n gʋlsa a sẽn yetã la D paas-a nangã pʋgẽ paasg tεkẽ."
  19,80,"La D rɩk a sẽn bɑsã fɑɑd n bɑs-ɑ tɑ wa Tõnd nengẽ beelle."
  19,81,"Lɑ b gãda zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnd n maan b soab-rãmba, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ b yɩ b sõngdbɑ."
  19,82,"Pɑ woto ye, b na n wa kɩfla ne b tũudmã la b yɩ b bεεba."
  19,83,"Fo pa ne tɩ Tõnd n tʋmsd Sʋtãambã kɩfr-rãmbẽ wã tɩ b lengd-b [n tʋg tʋʋm beedẽ wã] lengr tεkẽ?"
  19,84,"Bɩ f Ra yãg ne-b ye, ad Tõnd geendɑ b yõyã geelg tεkẽ, tɩ sã n wɑ sɑ bɩ D yõk-bɑ."
  19,85,"(Tẽeg) raar ning D sẽn na n wa tigim wẽn-zoεtbã n kẽng Yolsg naab nengẽ, tɩ b yaa zãma sẽn tɑr wɑoore."
  19,86,"La D kãag kɩfr-rãmbã n kẽng Gεhannem tɩ b yɑɑ ko-yũud rãmbɑ."
  19,87,"B pa tar sugsd rẽnda ned ning sẽn rɩk-a pʋleng dũni ne yolsg Naɑbã n kõ sɩd lɑ mɑɑn neere."
  19,88,"La b (yɑhʋʋd-rãmb lɑ nɑsɑɑr-dãmbɑ) yeelɑme tɩ: "" yolsg naabã tara biiga""."
  19,89,"Ad yãmb wa ne yel-kisg sẽn yaa bedre."
  19,90,"Saasã tʋll n pãrsame gom-kãngã yĩnga tɩ tẽngã tʋll n pus n pãrse tɩ tãnsã tʋll n wur wurb tεkẽ."
  19,91,"B sẽn yeel tɩ yolsg Naabã tara biigã yĩnga."
  19,92,"La pa sõmb ne yolsg Naabã t'A wa tar biig ye."
  19,93,"Ad bũmb ning sẽn be saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã fãa wata yolsg Naab nengẽ tɩ b yaa yembse n gãneg b mense."
  19,94,"Ad A minim gũbg-b lame la A sõd-b-lɑ sõdb tεkẽ."
  19,95,"Lɑ b yembr fãɑ na n waa A nengẽ Yikr raarã t'ɑ yaa ɑ yembre."
  19,96,"Ad neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã la b tʋm tʋʋm sõma wã, yolsg Naabã na n maan-b-lɑ nonglem."
  19,97,"Ad Tõnd yols-ɑ-la (Kʋrãanã) ne ɑ sẽn sɩg ne fo zɩlemdã, sẽn na yɩl tɩ fo noog wẽn-zoεtbã sũur la f bugs ne-ɑ kokor-kegems rãmba."
  19,98,"Lɑ sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk neb sẽn deng bãmbã taoore, sẽn yaa zãma; rẽ yĩnga fo tara ned baa a yembr kɩbare, bɩ fo wʋmda b wũn-wũni?"
